on Film Critics Society Award for Best Actress|Best Actress]]\n| [[Lupita Nyong'o]]\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| Best Original Score\n| [[Michael Abels]]\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=\"5\" style=\"text-align:center;\"| [[IndieWire Critics Poll]]<ref name=\"icp19\">{{cite web | url=https://www.indiewire.com/2019/12/best-movies-2019-critics-survey-poll-performances-parasite-adam-driver-lupita-nyongo-1202197615/ | title=2019 Critics Poll: The Best Films and Performances According to Over 300 Critics From Around the World | publisher=[[Indiewire]]| accessdate=December 16, 2019|author= Kohn, Eric}}</ref>\n| scope=\"row\" rowspan=\"5\" style=\"text-align:center;\"|December 16, 2019\n| Best Film\n| ''Us''\n| {{no|15th Place}}\n|-\n| Best Actress\n| [[Lupita Nyong'o]]\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Best Director\n| rowspan=\"2\"| [[Jordan Peele]]\n| {{no|16th Place}}\n|-\n| Best Screenplay\n| {{no|11th Place}}\n|-\n| Best Cinematography \n| [[Mike Gioulakis]]\n| {{no|20th Place}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\"| [[International Cinematographers Guild]]<ref name=\"ICG20\">{{cite web|url=https://variety.com/2020/artisans/awards/irishman-joker-publicist-awards-1203460364/ |title=ICG Publicists Awards Unveil 2020 Nominations |publisher= [[Variety (magazine)|Variety]] |accessdate=January 8, 2020 |date=January 8, 2020| author= Tangay, Jazz}}</ref>\n| scope=\"row\"  style=\"text-align:center;\"|February 7, 2020\n| Maxwell Weinberg Publicist Showmanship Award\n| ''Us''\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\"| [[International Cinephile Society]]<ref name=\"ics20\">{{cite web | url=https://icsfilm.org/our-yearly-awards/2020-ics-award-winners/| title=Pain and Glory Makes a Splash at 17th ICS Awards| publisher=[[International Cinephile Society]]| accessdate=February 10, 2020}}</ref>\n| scope=\"row\"  style=\"text-align:center;\"|February 4, 2020\n| Best Actress\n| [[Lupita Nyong'o]]\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center; style=\"text-align: