 Actress|Outstanding Actress]]\n| [[Lupita Nyong'o]]\n| {{Won}}\n|-\n| [[Black Reel Award for Outstanding Director|Outstanding Director]]\n| [[Jordan Peele]]\n| {{Won}}\n|-\n| [[Black Reel Award for Outstanding Supporting Actress|Outstanding Supporting Actress]]\n| scope=\"row\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:left;\"| [[Shahadi Wright Joseph]]\n| {{Nom}}\n|-\n| Outstanding Breakthrough Performance \u2013 Female\n| {{Nom}}\n|-\n| [[Black Reel Award for Outstanding Screenplay, Adapted or Original|Outstanding Screenplay]]\n| [[Jordan Peele]]\n| {{Won}}\n|-\n| [[Black Reel Award for Outstanding Ensemble|Outstanding Ensemble]]\n| Terri Taylor \u2013 casting director\n| {{Nom}}\n|-\n| [[Black Reel Award for Outstanding Original Score|Outstanding Score]]\n| [[Michael Abels]]\n| {{Won}}\n|-\n| Outstanding Cinematography\n| [[Mike Gioulakis]]\n| {{Nom}}\n|-\n| Outstanding Costume Design\n| [[Kym Barrett]]\n| {{Nom}}\n|-\n| Outstanding Production Design\n| Ruth De Jong\n| {{Nom}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\"| [[BreakTudo Awards]]<ref name=\"BA19\">{{Cite web |url=https://www.breaktudo.com/breaktudo-awards-2019-anitta-e-ariana-grande-lideram-a-lista-de-indicados-com-5-indicacoes-cada/ |title=BreakTudo Awards 2019: Anitta e Ariana Grande lideram a lista de indicados com 5 indica\u00e7\u00f5es cadas|date=August 24, 2019 |website=[[BreakTudo Awards]] |access-date=September 21, 2019}}</ref>\n| scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\"| [[BreakTudo Awards 2019|October 20, 2019]]\n| Movie of the Year\n| ''Us''\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;\"| [[Chicago Film Critics Association]]<ref name=\"cfca19\">{{cite web | url=https://deadline.com/2019/12/chicago-film-critics-give-best-picture-to-parasite-1202809578/ | title=Chicago Film Critics Give Best Picture To \u2018Parasite\u2019 And Best Director To Bong Joon Ho| publisher=[[Deadline Hollywood]] | accessdate=December 14, 2019| author= Bennett,Anita}}</ref>\n| scope=\"row