ar)\n| [[Anjum Fakih]]\n|-\n| Best Actor in Negative Role Male (Popular)\n| [[Sanjay Gagnani]]\n|-\n| Best Actor in Negative Role Female (Popular)\n| Ruhi Chaturvedi\n|-\n| rowspan=9| [[Gold Awards]]\n| [[Gold Award for Best Actress in a Lead Role|Best Actress Female (Popular)]]\n| [[Shraddha Arya]]\n| {{won}}\n| rowspan=9|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://goldawards.in|title=Nominations for 12th Boroplus Gold Awards, 2019|website=12th Gold Awards}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Gold Award for Best Actor in a Lead Role|Best Actor Male (Popular)]]\n| [[Dheeraj Dhoopar]]\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Best Onscreen Jodi (Popular)\n| [[Shraddha Arya]] and [[Dheeraj Dhoopar]]\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| Best Actor in a Supporting Role (Female)\n| [[Anjum Fakih]]\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| Best Actor in a Supporting Role (Male)\n| [[Manit Joura]]\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| Best Actor in Negative Role Male (Popular)\n| rowspan=2|[[Sanjay Gagnani]]\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| Best Actor in Negative Role Male (Critics)\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Best Actress in Negative Role Female (Popular)\n| [[Ruhi Chaturvedi]]\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| Best TV Show (Popular)\n| [[Ekta Kapoor]]\n| {{won}}\n|-\n|rowspan=3|[[Indian Television Academy Awards]]\n|Best Actor (Popular)\n|[[Dheeraj Dhoopar]]\n| rowspan=2 {{won}}\n| rowspan=\"3\" | <ref>[https://www.bizasialive.com/ita-awards-2019-winners-list/ 19th ITA Awards, 2019: Winners List]</ref><ref>[https://www.latestly.com/entertainment/tv/ita-awards-2019-winners-list-kundali-bhagya-shivangi-joshi-dheeraj-dhoopar-kapil-sharma-win-big-at-the-indian-television-academy-awards-in-indore-1328289.html/amp 19th ITA Awards, 2019 Winners: Dheeraj Dhoopar, Sriti Jha, Kundali Bhagya wins top honours]</ref>\n|-\n| Best Show (Popular)\n| [[Ekta Kapoor]]\n|-\n| Best Actress (Popular)\n| [[Shraddha Arya]]\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"7\" |2020\n| rowspan=\"3\" | [[Kalakar Awards]]\n| Best Actor\n| [[Dheeraj Dhoopar]]\n| rowspan=\"1\" {{won}}\n| rowspan=\"3\" |<ref>[https://thekolkatamail.com/28th-annual-kalakar-awards-2020-to-take-place-on